title: Garmin MapSource 6.15.3 Special
description:
Garmin MapSource Special version 6.15.3

This modified executable will let you upload your mapset (gmapsupp.img) to your PC drives or your GPS.



Instructions for use:

- Install MapSource 6.15.3, get it from Garmin website: http://www8.garmin.com/support/download_details.jsp?id=209

- Replace mapsource.exe



Made by Nincsenex

(If you like it, please press the +82 next to "Quality:")
